'''2010年英聯邦運動會'''於2010年10月3日至14日在[[印度|印度]][[德里|德里]]舉行，该运动会的各项筹备工作饱受批评，包括体育场馆建设、保安问题等。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/sports/zonghe/detail_2010_09/29/2666819_0.shtml |title=印度英联邦运动会筹办乱像 建设拖沓腐败丑闻不断 |accessdate=2010-10-03 |archive-date=2010-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101003180928/http://news.ifeng.com/sports/zonghe/detail_2010_09/29/2666819_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

运动会的举办期间，印度运动员表现出色，取得了38金27银36铜的成绩，有媒體稱流畅的体育赛事和壮观的闭幕式在很大程度上掩盖了之前组织工作的不足。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.iol.co.za/sport/more-sport/cwg-spectacular-closing-ceremony-1.686264 |title=CWG: Spectacular closing ceremony |publisher=Independent Online (South Africa) |date=2010-11-13 |accessdate=2010-10-05 |archive-date=2010-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101017133607/http://www.iol.co.za/sport/more-sport/cwg-spectacular-closing-ceremony-1.686264 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/jamespearce/2010/10/did_delhi_live_up_to_expectati.html |title=Did Delhi live up to expectations? |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2010-10-14 |accessdate=2010-10-05 |archive-date=2011-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111222093345/http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/jamespearce/2010/10/did_delhi_live_up_to_expectati.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/sport/commonwealth-games/chaos-and-confusion-but-games-played-on/story-fn66fst6-1225938954091 |title=Chaos and confusion, but Games played on |newspaper=The Australian |date=2010-10-15 |accessdate=2010-10-05 |archive-date=2010-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101022150916/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/sport/commonwealth-games/chaos-and-confusion-but-games-played-on/story-fn66fst6-1225938954091 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在闭幕仪式上，[[英联邦运动会|英联邦运动会]]联合会主席宣布新德里主办了一次“真正的无与伦比的運動會”。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/cwgarticleshow/6750365.cms|title=Delhi has delivered a truly exceptional Games: Fennell|newspaper=Times of India|date=2010-10-14|accessdate=2010-10-05|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120720095525/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/cwgarticleshow/6750365.cms|archivedate=2012-07-20|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

