== 軼事 ==
除了来自外部的批评，印度民众也批评运动会的筹备工作。[[印度斯坦时报|印度斯坦时报]]23日公布的民意调查显示，68%的受访[[新德里|新德里]]居民为这届运动会感到丢脸。另外印度媒体以国家耻辱为标题报道此次运动会。

一场精彩的开幕式扭转了英联邦运动会带给印度的负面形象，曾质疑印度是否有能力举办英联邦运动会的外国记者，亦纷纷赞扬那是他们见过最棒的开幕式之一。国际奥委会主席罗格表示，印度为申办奥运会主办权打下的良好基础。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/sport/2010/oct/03/commonwealth-games-opening-ceremony-delhi-india |title='India has arrived': spectacular ceremony opens Commonwealth Games |publisher=The Guardian, UK |date=2010-10-03 |accessdate=2010-10-05 |archive-date=2010-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101006004503/http://www.guardian.co.uk/sport/2010/oct/03/commonwealth-games-opening-ceremony-delhi-india |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/othersports/commonwealthgames/8039988/Commonwealth-Games-2010-India-opens-doors-to-the-world-at-opening-ceremony.html |title=Commonwealth Games 2010: India opens doors to the world at opening ceremony |publisher=The Telegraph |date=2010-10-03 |accessdate=2010-10-05 |archive-date=2010-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101006045221/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/othersports/commonwealthgames/8039988/Commonwealth-Games-2010-India-opens-doors-to-the-world-at-opening-ceremony.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://cwg.ndtv.com/commonwealth/article/id/spoen20100155419/type/latest/India-should-aim-for-Olympics-Australian-Sports-Minister-57139.html|date=2010-10-05|title=India should aim for Olympics: Australian Sports Minister|accessdate=2010-10-05|publisher=NDTV|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101008201707/http://cwg.ndtv.com/commonwealth/article/id/spoen20100155419/type/latest/India-should-aim-for-Olympics-Australian-Sports-Minister-57139.html|archivedate=2010-10-08}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Games good foundation for Olympic bid by India: Rogge|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/cwgarticleshow/6680736.cms|date=2010-10-04|publisher=Times of India|accessdate=2010-10-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101006222100/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/cwgarticleshow/6680736.cms|archivedate=2010-10-06|deadurl=yes}}